                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": "The kids and I had a blast playing Baba is You this morning, and it brought up ancient memories of playing Sokoban puzzles  (where all you can do push crates around; in particular no pulling). Now I want to play Sokoban on my phone.\n\n"
