                                {
                                    "type": "link",
                                    "url": "https:\/\/lcamtuf.coredump.cx\/sir-box-a-lot"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "text": " contains 300 publicly available Sokoban puzzles. It turns out the C syntax that those puzzles are encoded in is just a few search-and-replaces from being perfectly valid and usable Lua. So far I can render the starting state."
